import React from 'react' export default function DisplayWeather(props) { const { location, country, temp, maxTemp, minTemp, main, description, icon, humidity, windSpeed, clouds, sunrise, sunset, } = props.weatherData; return (
{location}
{country}
{temp}
{maxTemp}
{minTemp} {main}
{description}
{icon}
{humidity}
{windSpeed}
{clouds}
{sunrise}
{sunset}
) }
